testcase.name: ApplicationController .create should create a book in the database
ApplicationController .create should produce a bad request if invalid data
ApplicationController .read should find a book in the database by id
ApplicationController .read should produce a bad request if no valid data
ApplicationController .readByName() should find a book by its name
ApplicationController .readByCopies should return all books with more than 50 copies
ApplicationController .update() should update a book by id
ApplicationController .update() should produce a bad request if bad update data
ApplicationController .update() should produce a bad request if no such data to update
ApplicationController .updateByField should return a DataModel with a changed name
ApplicationController .updateByField should return a DataModel with more copies sold
ApplicationController .delete() should return bad request if no such id
addBookForm should return a valid response
